cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as object categorization and 3D pose estimation from 2D images. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new architecture for the task, which involves training multiple networks, indicating a possible overlap with robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the experiments involve working with images, suggesting a possible connection with multimedia (cs.MM).
